Module me.sbasalaev.tybyco

Package me.sbasalaev.tybyco.builders

package me.sbasalaev.tybyco.builders
Builders for class elements. All builders implement fluent interface. Unless noted otherwise, the builder should not be used after any method is called on it. Instead, the result of the method should be used for subsequent operations.
